2011-05-13  Juan Pablo Santos (juanpablo AT apache DOT org)
        
        * 3.0.0-svn-230
        
        * JSPWIKI-691: Navigation to ./admin/Admin.jsp with a non-authorized user redirects to a blank ./Message.jsp. 
        
