        David Au.
        
        * [JSPWIKI-169]: Fix to allow mail sender from JNDI in addition
        to property file.  Thanks to Dave Wolf.
        
        * [JSPWIKI-177]: Completely overhauled German translation, thanks
        to Florian Holeczek.

